\[\sup_{|x-1|\leq\frac{1}{4}}|(\hat{q})^{\prime}(x)|\leq M_{\gamma}^{\prime} \cdot\int_{0}^{\infty}|\hat{q}(x)|w_{\gamma}(x)\,dx\leq\frac{M_{\gamma}^{\prime }}{C^{\prime}}\cdot\mathbb{E}_{X\sim\mathcal{D}}\left[|q(X)|\right].\]

