\[\mathbb{E}_{X\sim\mathcal{D}}\left[|q(X)|\right]\leq 1+1=2.\]

By Proposition 39, this means that, for some constant \(C_{\mathcal{D}}>1\) depending only on \(\mathcal{D}\),

\[\sup_{|x|\leq\frac{1}{4}}|q^{\prime}(x)|\leq 2\cdot C_{\mathcal{D}}.\]

